title: Sweep/Buy 10 Floor BAYC after auction ends
body:
Since this proposal passed quorum after auction ended, but before the expiry date of quorum deadline, we can look to put this as a snapshot vote anyhow. 

Reasoning: BAYC's are seeming to be holding up well (their floor price) during these tumultuous times and they have an extremely strong community

Proposed by: 3SlashMDos
